
Script files:

basicif.m:
    demonstrate using if-else-end statement

branch.m: examples of using if-end and if-else-end branching control flow.
    Also shows using approximate equality in comparing non-integer numbers.

grades.m:
    using if-elseif and switch-case to determine grades

flop_equality.m:
    a warning about testing for exact equality 

Be sure to read and run them. Also be sure to experiment with them, and fully
understand what is happening in them. Some questions and suggestions for
modification are in the comments - answer those and try the modifications. The
goal is to be comfortable with everything that is done in them (minus one or
two exceptions explicitly identified in the comments)

